INTELLIPLANT AI TECHNICAL MANUAL — ALFA LAVAL HX-7 HEAT EXCHANGER
Document Ref: TM-HX7-003 | Version: v1.4 | Asset Code: HX-7 | Location: Plant B

1. OPERATIONAL RATING & SPECIFICATIONS
- Model: Alfa Laval M10-MFM Plate Heat Exchanger
- Design Pressure: 16 bar
- Design Temperature: 150°C
- Gasket Material: EPDM Clip-on Gaskets (Item Code: GSK-100)
- Heat Transfer Area: 48.5 m²

2. CRITICAL WARNINGS & FOULING MONITORING
- RUL Critical Status: Currently rated at 52 Days RUL due to thermal stress and channel fouling.
- Clean-In-Place (CIP) Flushing Interval: Every 6 months using 2% Nitric Acid solution at 60°C.
- Hydrostatic Test Pressure: 24 bar for 30 minutes following any plate pack disassembly.